Class AdvancedConfigurationTab

  • java.lang.Object
    • ui.AdvancedConfigurationTab

  • public class AdvancedConfigurationTab
extends java.lang.Object
    AdvancedConfigurationTab is the class that creates a tab to the frame that will allow the user to configure the variables and the algorithm to resolve the problem.
    Author:
    Nuno Fialho EIC1 72910, Sandro Ferreira EIC1 72911, Duarte Pinto EIC1 73117
